<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f9f3; color: #243313; margin: 0; padding: 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(36,51,19,0.08);">
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #77b81e, #5d9516); color: #ffffff; padding: 24px 28px;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 26px;">Order Confirmed</h1>
            <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; opacity: 0.92;">Thanks for shopping with AgriCloud.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 28px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0;">Hello {{ order.customer.name }},</p>
            <p>Your order <strong>#{{ order.id }}</strong> has been confirmed. We attached a PDF summary with the full order details for your records.</p>

            <div style="border: 1px solid #dfe8d0; border-radius: 14px; background: #fbfcf8; padding: 18px; margin: 22px 0;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Product:</strong> {{ order.product.name }}</div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Quantity:</strong> {{ order.quantity }} {{ order.product.unit }}</div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Total:</strong> {{ order.totalPrice }} TND</div>
                <div><strong>Shipping to:</strong> {{ order.shippingAddress }}, {{ order.shippingCity }}{% if order.shippingPostal %} {{ order.shippingPostal }}{% endif %}</div>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">We will keep you updated as the order moves forward.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
